item.title: CVE-2024-1144|2024-03-19T11:32:49.261Z -- devklan -- alma%20blog
item.description: Improper access control vulnerability in Devklan's Alma Blog that affects versions 2.1.10 and earlier. This vulnerability could allow an unauthenticated user to access the application's functionalities without the need for credentials.
